title: Neuro-Programmer 3.2.6 Portable
description:
Neuro-Programmer 3.2.6 Portable| 66.8 MB

Neuro-Programmer 3 is a flexible but easy to use software application for stimulating the brain, improving your mental abilities and achieving lasting personal change. Using this tool, you control your mind.

The many uses of NP3:
We're constantly scouring the scientific literature and consulting with leading experts and researchers in the field to ensure that NP3 is always based on the latest knowledge.

We draw directly from the protocols used in peer-reviewed research to successfully and significantly:
* Reduce stress and anxiety
* Sharpen focus and concentration
* Improve cognition and provide study help
* Increase energy and motivation
* Strengthen emotional stability and mental health

OS : Windows 2000/XP/Vista/7/8

Language : English
